title: Star Trek Discovery s01 fanedits
description:
Star Trek Discover Season one episodes 1-9 fanedits. 

Oh man, this had to be done. 

At first, me and my buddies all watching the show. 


3 episodes later, half left. I was defending the show, saying it's still good for a watch. The production values! 

By the 7th episode, I was alone. No one else was with me. 

So this is the result, this edit is for ones who would like the show to be a bit more like the old show. 

No swear words, less violence, less focus on the main character. That type of thing. 

I hope you enjoy!
